Summary: Went out front of my house and saw five lights in a triangle shape with a flashing red/orange light in the center
divs: sighting detailsi walked out front of my house at 10:30pm and the object immediately caught my eye, it was flying very low and had no sound, 5 lights in a triangle\ warped rectangle shape with a red pulsating light in the center. i watched the object fly from west to east over west wichita. i saw other airplanes in the area and also saw and heard jet aircraft very high in altitude, all the planes i saw in the area had flashing red and blue lights with a strobe like characteristics. "normal looking" this object had a very slow pulsating red and orange light in the center and looked very abnormal and different than any other aircraft i've seen before.
